Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:20.56,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur3}曾经我这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.82,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{\blur3}今天不想见你
